<br>
Bring Fish Scales and teach the people how to PULL from the water (enduring breath spell)  That is the BEST way to find Crocs there.<br>
<br>
Keep CURE DISEASE Memmed.  Lots of Undead casting Rabies and the like.<br>
<br>
